<plot>Throughout "Hill of Happiness" you get a sneak peak into Lee Hayes' life. He is currently attending an all boys high school with his older brother Ethan. During this time a tragic event happens in their family and they are stuck dealing with it in this strict Catholic environment. With the support of Lee's friend James and the overall support of St. Lawrence, Lee and Ethan learn to deal with the matter at hand with a mature attitude. This is a true story and is played by real people in real locations.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?239537</url></doc>
